headline: Did Record Q4 Results and a New Tokenization Platform Just Shift State Street's (STT) Investment Narrative?
summary: State Street Corporation has reported past fourth-quarter 2025 results with record revenue and year-on-year growth in net interest income to US$802 million, alongside slightly lower net income of US$747 million, and has also launched a new Digital Asset Platform to support tokenized funds and cash products for institutional clients. Beyond the headline earnings beat, State Street’s push into tokenization infrastructure suggests a meaningful effort to align its core custody and servicing...
